flowchart TD
    Start([START: User adds/updates milestone with dependencies]) --> GetMilestones[Get list of all milestone IDs in goal]
    GetMilestones --> ForEachDep[For each dependency ID]
    
    ForEachDep --> CheckExists{Dependency ID exists in milestone list?}
    CheckExists -->|NO| Error1[ERROR: Dependency references non-existent milestone]
    Error1 --> End1([END])
    CheckExists -->|YES| CheckCircular[Check for circular dependencies]
    
    CheckCircular --> BuildGraph[Build dependency graph]
    BuildGraph --> RunCycleDetection[Run cycle detection algorithm DFS]
    RunCycleDetection --> CycleResult{Cycle detected?}
    CycleResult -->|YES| Error2[ERROR: Circular dependencies detected]
    Error2 --> End2([END])
    CycleResult -->|NO| CheckSelf[Check: milestone depends on itself?]
    
    CheckSelf --> SelfDep{Milestone depends on itself?}
    SelfDep -->|YES| Error3[ERROR: Milestone cannot depend on itself]
    Error3 --> End3([END])
    SelfDep -->|NO| ValidationPassed[Validation passed]
    
    ValidationPassed --> SaveMilestone[Save milestone]
    SaveMilestone --> End4([END: Dependencies valid, milestone saved])

    style Start fill:#e1f5ff
    style End1 fill:#ffcdd2
    style End2 fill:#ffcdd2
    style End3 fill:#ffcdd2
    style End4 fill:#c8e6c9
    style CheckExists fill:#fff9c4
    style CycleResult fill:#fff9c4
    style SelfDep fill:#fff9c4

